        <div class="problem-cause">Burner lights and extinguishes — the most common La Cornue service call. The French-spec thermocouple generates millivolt current that holds the safety valve open. We test output before replacing. La Cornue thermocouples are specific to the burner configuration and series — correct replacement requires confirming the range model and production date.</div>
