        <div class="problem-cause">Vaulted dome thermostat drift or door gasket seal failure. Dome-specific calibration required — standard single-point temperature readings don't accurately characterize a vaulted oven. We use multi-point measurement across the dome. Door gasket seal failure at coastal properties accelerates: salt air degrades gasket compression faster inland. Serial number determines correct replacement gasket specification.</div>
